      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nJWGLDoa47mPF24CtJTXu6-1280-80.jpg\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nJWGLDoa47mPF24CtJTXu6-1280-80.jpg\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nJWGLDoa47mPF24CtJTXu6-1280-80.jpg\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\nDIYer shows how they made a handsome magnetic core memory USB drive using home CNC and 3D printing equipment. However, it isn't a homebrew answer to the AI-induced memory crisis with only 64 bits of data capacity",
