    {
      "id": "https://linuxcommunity.io/t/welcome-introduce-yourself/6712?page=45#post_904",
      "url": "https://linuxcommunity.io/t/welcome-introduce-yourself/6712?page=45#post_904",
      "title": "[Kagi Small Web] Welcome! Introduce yourself",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://linuxcommunity.io/uploads/default/original/2X/c/c4176b9131f819ae9a48fd272c3d20555d4b3126.png\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<img src=\"https://linuxcommunity.io/uploads/default/original/2X/c/c4176b9131f819ae9a48fd272c3d20555d4b3126.png\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<img src=\"https://linuxcommunity.io/uploads/default/original/2X/c/c4176b9131f819ae9a48fd272c3d20555d4b3126.png\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<img src=\"https://linuxcommunity.io/uploads/default/original/2X/c/c4176b9131f819ae9a48fd272c3d20555d4b3126.png\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<img src=\"https://linuxcommunity.io/uploads/default/original/2X/c/c4176b9131f819ae9a48fd272c3d20555d4b3126.png\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<p>I don’t recall the year, but my first experience with Linux was with a Slackware distro that arrived on 3.5\" floppy disks. I compiled a kernel specific to my 386DX machine. It took a l-o-n-g time but the end result was a slightly faster machine.</p>\n<p>Later in another job at a small company, I was the defacto IT Department mostly because I was also the electronics guy. After that and until I retired I worked at a company developing products that ran embedded Linux systems. We used Ubuntu as our cross-development platform. We also had some production product testers in the factory that were built around Raspberry Pi SBCs.</p>\n<p>My home NAS is a Raspberry Pi 4 running Ubuntu Server and I also have a small H-P EliteDesk that runs Home Assistant OS.</p>\n<p>Tim</p>",
      "date_published": "2026-07-04T01:35:59+00:00",
      "authors": [
        {
          "name": "Kagi Small Web",
          "url": "https://kagi.com/smallweb"
        }
      ],
      "image": "https://linuxcommunity.io/uploads/default/original/2X/c/c4176b9131f819ae9a48fd272c3d20555d4b3126.png",
      "_score": 3,
      "_quality": 3,
      "_relevance": 3,
      "_local_score": 0
    },
